OL,6,FThey could restart exercise with
OL,7,F"gentle" walks, which they can do with
OL,8,Ftheir babies, and then increase to
OL,9,F"moderate" activity when they are
OL,10,Fready, they added.
OL,12,FThis moderate physical activity could
OL,13,Finclude brisk walking, water aerobics,
OL,14,Fstationary cycling or resistance
OL,15,Ftraining, according to a team of
OL,16,Facademics in Canada.
OL,18,FThe researchers pooled data from
OL,19,Favailable evidence on the impact of
OL,20,Fexercise after childbirth.
