OL,3,CExercise can help cut risk of 'baby
OL,4,Cblues' ` study
OL,6,FTheir new study, published in the
OL,7,FBritish Journal of Sports Medicine,
OL,8,Fexamined 35 studies involving more
OL,9,Fthan 4,000 women from 14 different
OL,10,Fcountries.
OL,12,FThe odds of postpartum depression were
OL,13,Freduced by 45% among those who engaged
OL,14,Fin exercise compared to those who did
OL,15,Fnot.
OL,17,FAnd exercise was associated with less
OL,18,Fsevere symptoms of depression and
OL,19,Fanxiety after giving birth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
