OL,3,CExercise can help cut risk of 'baby
OL,4,Cblues' ` study
OL,6,FStarting exercise before 12 weeks
OL,7,Fafter birth was linked to a greater
OL,8,Freduction in depressive symptoms than
OL,9,Fstarting it later.
OL,11,FAnd the greater the exercise volume
OL,12,Fthe greater the reduction in the
OL,13,Fseverity of symptoms, the research
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,16,FTo reap the benefits of exercise,
OL,17,Fwomen should try and engage in at
OL,18,Fleast 80 minutes of moderate intensity
OL,19,Fexercise each week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
