OL,6,FAnd they should try to be moderately
OL,7,Factive on at least four days of the
OL,8,Fweek.
OL,10,FLead author Professor Margie
OL,11,FDavenport, from the University of
OL,12,FAlberta, told the PA news agency:
OL,13,FWhile historical recommendations
OL,14,Fsuggest waiting for six weeks before
OL,15,Fstarting moderate to vigorous
OL,16,Fintensity exercise, more recent work
OL,17,Fhas suggested that early mobilisation
OL,18,Fand incorporation of light intensity
OL,19,Fphysical activity such as gentle
OL,20,Fwalking can facilitate postpartum
OL,21,Frecovery."
