OL,6,FShe added: "Once (the mother) has
OL,7,Frecovered from labour and delivery,
OL,8,Fgoing for short gentle walks is
OL,9,Fencouraged.
OL,11,F"Walking is a great way to get
OL,12,Fexercise, and it's something you can
OL,13,Fdo with your baby.
OL,15,F"As she is ready to begin more
OL,16,Fvigorous exercise, we recommend a
OL,17,Fgradual but progressive fashion.
