OL,6,F"It's important that attention is paid
OL,7,Fto symptoms such as poor recovery
OL,8,Fafter exercise which may mean that
OL,9,Fexercise is progressing too quickly.
OL,11,F"Those who experience urinary
OL,12,Fincontinence are recommended to speak
OL,13,Fto a pelvic floor physiotherapist for
OL,14,Fassessment and treatment.
OL,16,F"Everyone's ideal starting time will
OL,17,Fbe different balancing the need to
OL,18,Frecover and heal from childbirth with
OL,19,Freadiness to begin being physically
OL,20,Factive to derive both physical and
OL,21,Fmental health benefits."
